*** After a long visit to the pub, Joe was showing off his new apartment to his friend Bob, who was curious about a big brass gong in the bedroom. “It’s a talking clock,” said Joe. “How does it work?” asked Bob. “Watch,” said Joe.  

He picked up a hammer and gave the gong a mighty whack. From the other side of the wall came a furious shout, “Don’t you know it’s three o’ clock in the morning?”  

